	uqadaha badan\, waxay ku heesaan heeso waxayna la sameeyaan farshaxanka iy
	o farsamooyinka gacanta ee fudud daryeelayaashooda inta lagu jiro wakhtiga
	 kooxda.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nNewHolly Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Ro
	om\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required.\n\nDetailed Des
	cription: Kaleidoscope Play & Learn offers a chance for children and their
	 families to come play and have a good time.\, There is also a play time f
	or children to explore various toys and play activities.\, Children learn 
	and explore the use of art\, music\, toys and more. Families learn about t
	heir child&'s development and community resources available to them.\, Tha
	nks to our partner\n\nEast African Community Services .\,\n\n-------------
	--------------------------------------------------\, Ku ciyaarista iyo bar
	ashada qalabka Kaleidoscope-ka waxay siisaa fursad carruurta iyo qoysaskoo
	da ay isugu yimaadaan si ay u ciyaaraan oo ayna waqti fiican ku wada qaata
	an. Waxa kale oo jira wakhti ay carruurtu ku sahminayaan alaabta ay caruur
	tu ku ciyaaraan ee kala duwan iyo hawlaha ciyaarta. Carruurtu waxay bartaa
	n oona sahmiyaan isticmaalka farshaxanka\, muusiga\, alaabta ay caruurtu k
	u ciyaaraan iyo wax ka loo badan. Qoysasku waxay bartaan horumarka ilmahoo
	da iyo macluumaadka/ilaha bulshada ee ay heli karaan.\, Waxaa mahad leh la
	-hawlgalaheena\n\nAdeegyada Bulshada Bariga Afrika \\(East African Communi
	ty Services\\) .\n\nEvent Logistics: This group is open to children of all
	 abilities\, ages 0 - 5 years old.\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn is for Fami
	ly\, Friend & Neighbor Caregivers\, Parents\, and the children in their ca
	re. This is not a drop-off program and it is not agood fit for daycare cen
	ters\, preschools\, or other childcare organizations.\, Find out more abou
	t\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n\nprograms.\,\n\n-----------------------
	----------------------------------------\, Kooxdani waxay u furan tahay ca
	rruurta qabaan dhammaan awoodaha kala duwan\, da'doodu tahay 0 - 5 sano ji
	r. Kani maaha barnaamij meel-ka-dhigis ah oo kuma habboona xarumaha xannaa
	nada\, dugsiyada barbaarinta\, ama ururrada kale ee daryeelka carruurta.\,
