BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:faaQ-hj26zVYk6pnprKjK
SUMMARY:Shen Yun 2026
DTSTAMP:20260327T044813Z
DTSTART:20260402T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:The gong resounds\, the curtain opens\, and fairies emerge from
	 a sea of billowing clouds. Mongolians ride on horseback across grasslands
	 as vast as the sky. Dynasties rise and fall—as ancient legends of love\, 
	loss\, humor and valor unfold before your eyes.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecent
	er.com/events/event-calendar/shen-yun-2026-x47077\n\nFrom Seattle Center E
	vents
URL:https://www.seattlecenter.com/events/event-calendar/shen-yun-2026-x4707
	7
LOCATION:Marion Oliver McCaw Hall
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-center-events
CATEGORIES:Seattle Center Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:v4gHDzz_krSaDHsoFxCd5
SUMMARY:Mary Jane
DTSTAMP:20260327T044813Z
DTSTART:20260402T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Poignantly humorous and deeply cathartic\, this semi-autobiogra
	phical drama by Tony-nominated playwright Amy Herzog is a love letter to c
	aregivers and support systems of all kinds.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecenter.c
	om/events/event-calendar/mary-jane-x46020\n\nFrom Seattle Center Events
