	 on the benefits of using your Chamber Master access. We will also cover n
	etworking opportunities and advocacy that are available to you as a member
	 of the Renton Chamber of Commerce. This training session will equip you w
	ith the ability to navigate and utilize your MIC Tools to effectively prom
	ote your business reaching over 10k potential customers. Posting Jobs\, Ev
