	Held on Zoom\, these virtual conversations provide space for neighborhood 
	updates\, safety resources\, and open dialogue with local businesses and c
	ommunity partners. We meet on the second Thursday of every month at 10am-a
	ll are welcome to join the discussion. Zoom link sent after registering an
	d you can add this recurring meeting to your calendar below: ADD TO GOOGLE
	 CALENDAR ADD TO OUTLOOK CALENDAR Need a link to Jen&'s safety resources? 
	Click here. About GSBA: Capitol Hill GSBA: Capitol Hill provides business 
	development\, engagement\, and advocacy for Capitol Hill businesses and no
	nprofits who are committed to our collective economic vitality.\n\nhttps:/
	/seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/gsba-capitol-hill-monthly-safety-ca
	ll/18234875/2026-04-09T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
