	es\, conversation practice\, and cultural activities. No prior foreign lan
	guage experience is required\; ages 16+.\n\nEvery Thursday\, April 2 - May
	 28\n\nNOR1A: 5-6:30pm - NOR1A is for absolute beginners with no prior lan
	guage experience\n\nNOR1C: 6:45-8pm - NOR1C is for students who may know s
	ome basic Norwegian and want to grow their skills\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amc
